            "row_content": "<p>Premium organic matcha (multiple grades), loose leaf teas, superfood powders (taro, lion's mane, coffee cherry, molasses, and more), and artisan spices. Everything is carefully sourced and lab-tested. No filler, no fluff.</p>",
