            "row_content": "<p>Our matcha is sourced from premium organic farms and stone-ground to preserve flavor, color, and nutrients. We carry different grades for different uses — ceremonial for sipping, culinary for cooking and lattes. It's tested, it's real, and it's seriously good.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
